data.description: Talk about space! This mobile home is over 2100 sq feet and has been very well taken care of. New flooring and paint throughout. The primary bedroom is HUGE and has a large attached bath with separate walk in shower and tub. There's a large walk in closet as well. Tons of storage space throughout the home. Open floorplan with kitchen, living, and dining. Detached two car garage for parking or use as a shop. All sitting on over an acre. Call today to see this one!
